Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ga boku wo aishinuku koto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Truly loving myself{\i0}
