Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter where this journey takes us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are itsukarada?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when was it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honne ga yowane ni nattana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being honest became whining{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nigenai koto ga tsuyosa ni natta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Standing firm became strength{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa mitsukaranai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you found it yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jishin janaku jibun jishin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not confidence, your true self{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kitto mada sagasetenai wasuremono ga aruhazu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There must be something\NI've forgotten that I still haven't found{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto mada tsutaetenai tsutaetai kotoba{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Words I want to say\NThat I still haven't said{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mitete kurerunara misete miserunoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you would watch me, I'd captivate you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ga boku wo aishinuku koto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Truly loving myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa mada shinjitemo iika?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it alright to still believe in that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kusuburuno wa chanto moeta karada{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I smolder because I've actually burned{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doko e mukau tabi datoshitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter where this journey takes us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada me wo mihiraite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just open my eyes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yume wo miru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And dream my dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yume wo shiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And know my dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,LAND RIDER LARHART
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?! I bet it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're braver than I thought.\NThat pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to fight back! While I still have\Nstamina and Magic Power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I like that face right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'll do what you did to Ruud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow your head off like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's the look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep that face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. I'm saved by\Nthe last guy I want saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should thank you, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So that man is the Hyunckel\NMaster Baran spoke of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, it looks like you've been\Noverextending yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to stop your enemies alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a choice in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's memories have been erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,by his father, Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Dai and Baran\Nare related by blood after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what's this\Nabout his memories being erased?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's Baran?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He went ahead to get Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we don't have time to waste\Non these scrubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That cocky bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Former Undead Legion Commander\Nof the Dark Army or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he's just a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slice you up just like that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay him back for what he did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?\NI'll be taking your spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That battered little kid can't fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can beat Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If by chance you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is a complete moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're letting the guy you saved die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'll finish the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll be coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I need are two more spells!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope my Magic Power holds out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Toberura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke!\NYou want to fight me in the air?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you can't beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hit you with my Bloody Sukuraido!.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It leaves a mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have the rest of my Magic Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Galdandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But my Magic Power's all empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attitude sucks,\Nbut I know how strong you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll be taking you up\Non getting some rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You truly did a good job, Popp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you! How dare you\Ndo that to Galdandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NThis time, I, Borahorn shall...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Borahorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an imposing Aura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...but after what you did\Nto my junior disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,don't expect to walk away from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You broke my precious fangs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pulverize you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fight already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat! You think you're so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The strength of Sea Rider Borahorn\Nis unrivaled in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Taste it for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Where does such a frail body\Nhide such strength?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think that this is\N"unrivaled in the world"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend has\Ntwice the strength in his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Weren't you going to pulverize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Glacial Breath!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That should finish it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Borahorn's Glacial Breath\Nis as strong as a Mahiado spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I strike someone when they're\Nfrozen solid by my Glacial Breath...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they shatter like glass!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is how I've always won!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As promised, I'll pulverize you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that? What is he doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, he can't do anything! How could he?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now shatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My Glacial Breath didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Play time is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the enemy\Nhas decreased in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't assume I'm like the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, my armour\Nrepels attack spells and breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was made by Ron Berku,\Nthe greatest craftsman in the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Dark Armour Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a gift. I don't know who made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't bluffing just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very good at spells.\NMore importantly, my weapon rivals yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look\Nat Ron Berku's other masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Armour Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Amudo!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}BLOODY SUKURAIDO{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}BEHOMA{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAL-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Amudo!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The same armour as me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we're equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm a better warrior,\Nso I guess I have the advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown me your best attack.\NI should repay in kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now see my best attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that was a decent dodge,\Nbut that was merely a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at your helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You claimed to be the greatest swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but can you do that with a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right. Without terrifying speed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and needle-point accuracy,\Nsuch a feat is impossible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he did it without even\Nscratching my forehead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, you're a powerful swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But your blade is all muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wanted to, I could easily\Npierce your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,before you finished blinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubbish! If you really can do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,then let's see you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Wave Slash, the fastest Avan Style\Nattack can't even scratch him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That appears to be your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You have power in your attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But even with that power,\Nunless you can hit me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same as before!\NI can't see his strikes at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just a flash of light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! I have to do something\Nabout his attacks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never see my attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, as promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall pierce your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's on a completely different level\Nthan the other two!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trying to see\Nthose speed attacks... is impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You still haven't given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a gamble,\Nbut I'll have to let him hit me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and strike back while he's not moving!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can withstand his attack\Nand pull him in,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then I just unleash\Nmy Bloody Sukuraido! straight ahead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My attacks are more devastating than his!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall end it with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He merely threw his gauntlet at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not foolish enough\Nto fall for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!\NThe Land Rider's most powerful strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Hakendisutoru!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unbelievable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing I could do worked on him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are only human after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something strange with the enemy?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Let me try my crystal ball again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell. I know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino, no matter where they hide you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can detect where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For we are connected\Nby our bond of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baran slowly makes his way to Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Popp and Hyunckel fall before\Nthe Dragon Masters trying to protect Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eventually Larhart begins to tell\Nthe story of Baran's astonishing past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why was Dai separated from his parents?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And what was the sad fate\Nof Dai's mother, Soala?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.51,0:23:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dai's Secret"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
